Module org.apache.jena.arq
Package org.apache.jena.riot

Interface WriterDatasetRIOT

All Known Implementing Classes:
JsonLD11Writer, NQuadsWriter, NullWriter, TriGWriter, TriGWriterBase, TriGWriterBlocks, TriGWriterFlat, TriGWriterLong, WriterDatasetProtobuf, WriterDatasetRIOTBase, WriterDatasetThrift, WriterTriX
public interface WriterDatasetRIOT
A RIOT serializer for a language. This covers both graphs and datasets. A WriterRIOT is a one-time use object (they may accumulate state, e.g. pretty writers).
